[EDIT ADD: Oops I meant the equivalent of the current 51 points in terms of purchasing power toward 1492 armor.  The future upgrades will cost at least twice as much--3k or up, so 105 points will be about the same as 51.  LDON has an INHERENT increase in challenge and cost in APs.  This can make it seem like a grind.  One reason I suggested more story line and component drops that will enhance story lines.  DKP is all about numbers; I like story with DKP in the background.]</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Ladwen on Mon Aug 02, 2004 6:37 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
