                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">But you better believe I'm going to voice my disinterest when someone suggests a change in the game to make LDoN scale in a way that nothing in EQ ever has before.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
