Does the ability of ldon to dynamically scale with the level of the people in the adventure not suggest that ldon could 'scale in a way nothing in eq ever has before'?  No content in eq has ever been usable by level 20's and level 65's before.  Ldon is new technology and presents a new zone design paradigm upon which soe can expand.
<br />

<br />
Hopefully ldon isn't the last expansion of its kind.  Even better would be if they managed to integrate the current ldon with future ldon-like expansions at least in terms of the point system.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />-<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=648415" target="_blank" class="postlink">Londo Mollari</a>
